snippet.title: Game & Watch - Donkey Kong Jr. (tabletop / panorama type) (c)1983 Nintendo [MAME emulation footage]
snippet.description: Support for this was added in MAME 0.211, thanks to algestam for the emulation and hydef for the artwork.  Artwork can be found at https://drive.google.com/open?id=1WLKcvynl0ky2mRL1UacA9yaiMTnNs4x5
